    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144631_4_35503-35544",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "35503-35544",
      "markText": "在阿尔及尔引起轰动。被捕的是一家商贸公司的年轻职员，他在海滩上杀害了一个阿拉伯人。",
      "totalCount": 936,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144631&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=35503&rangeEnd=35544",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fe532590813ab9effg011133?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=35503&rangeEnd=35544"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144631_5_4446-4540",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4446-4540",
      "markText": "他们就是这样，跌落在顶峰和深渊之间，上不上下不下，飘浮在那里，哪儿像活着，只是一天天毫无方向地混日子，沉湎于枯燥乏味的回忆，形同漂泊的幽灵，想要汲取点力量，也只能接受扎根在痛苦的土壤里了。",
      "totalCount": 768,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144631&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4446&rangeEnd=4540",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fe532590813ab9effg011133?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4446&rangeEnd=4540"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144631_4_2431-2445",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2431-2445",
      "markText": "一个人生了病，就陷入了孤独。",
      "totalCount": 748,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144631&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2431&rangeEnd=2445",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fe532590813ab9effg011133?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2431&rangeEnd=2445"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144631_5_3129-3209",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3129-3209",
      "markText": "有些男人自以为在爱情上十分轻浮，现在又找回忠贞不贰了。有些做儿子的，生活在母亲身边却视而不见，现在看到母亲的脸上多一条皱纹，便勾起种种回忆，感到极大的不安和悔恨",
      "totalCount": 738,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144631&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3129&rangeEnd=3209",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fe532590813ab9effg011133?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3129&rangeEnd=3209"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144631_4_3528-3584",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3528-3584",
      "markText": "四月十六日上午，贝尔纳·里厄大夫走出诊所，到楼梯平台中间绊到了一只死老鼠，当即一脚踢开，也并没在意，就下楼去了。",
      "totalCount": 728,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144631&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3528&rangeEnd=3584",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fe532590813ab9effg011133?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3528&rangeEnd=3584"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144631_5_6304-6388",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "6304-6388",
      "markText": "他所表达的，确是他多日思虑和苦楚的由衷之言，他想要传递的形象，也是在等待和情欲之火上长时间炖出来的。对方则相反，想象这是一种常见的激情、市场上叫卖的痛苦、系列化的忧伤。",
      "totalCount": 697,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144631&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6304&rangeEnd=6388",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fe532590813ab9effg011133?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6304&rangeEnd=6388"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144631_4_17096-17152",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "17096-17152",
      "markText": "怎么办才能避免浪费时间呢？答案：在时间的长河中体验。方法：在牙科医生的候诊室里，坐在一张不舒服的椅子上度过几天；",
      "totalCount": 629,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144631&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=17096&rangeEnd=17152",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fe532590813ab9effg011133?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=17096&rangeEnd=17152"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144631_4_24490-24550",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "24490-24550",
      "markText": "毫无疑问，一场战争肯定是愚蠢到家了，但是愚蠢并不妨碍战争会持续很久。人若是不总为个人着想，那么就会发觉，原来愚蠢是常态。",
      "totalCount": 629,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144631&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=24490&rangeEnd=24550",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fe532590813ab9effg011133?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=24490&rangeEnd=24550"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144631_4_1370-1430",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1370-1430",
      "markText": "在这里，四季的嬗变，仅仅在天空显现。只有清爽的空气、小贩从郊区运来的大批花篮，才带来春天的消息：那是在市场上兜售的春天。",
      "totalCount": 616,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144631&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1370&rangeEnd=1430",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fe532590813ab9effg011133?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1370&rangeEnd=1430"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144631_4_16843-16877",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "16843-16877",
      "markText": "小老头就朝小猫吐痰，又狠又准，如果有一口痰击中目标，他就嘿嘿笑起来。",
      "totalCount": 611,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144631&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=16843&rangeEnd=16877",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fe532590813ab9effg011133?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=16843&rangeEnd=16877"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144631_8_16521-16554",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "16521-16554",
      "markText": "无疑正因为如此，早晨接到妻子去世的消息，里厄大夫才表现得如此平静。",
      "totalCount": 598,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144631&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=16521&rangeEnd=16554",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fe532590813ab9effg011133?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=16521&rangeEnd=16554"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144631_5_3932-3958",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3932-3958",
      "markText": "他们会体验到想象力最终要给相信未来的人所造成的伤害。",
      "totalCount": 576,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144631&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3932&rangeEnd=3958",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fe532590813ab9effg011133?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3932&rangeEnd=3958"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144631_4_1684-1775",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1684-1775",
      "markText": "他们首先经营的是买卖，自不待言，他们也同样喜爱寻常的乐趣，他们爱女人，爱看电影，爱泡海水澡。不过，他们却十分理智，这类消遣只留待星期六晚上和星期天，而一周的其他日子，就力求多多赚钱。",
      "totalCount": 560,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144631&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1684&rangeEnd=1775",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fe532590813ab9effg011133?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1684&rangeEnd=1775"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144631_4_42000-42074",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "42000-42074",
      "markText": "死亡人数重又达到了三十来例的那天，贝尔纳·里厄看着官方电文，省长递给他电文时还说了一句：“他们害怕了。”只见电文上写道：“宣布鼠疫流行。全城封闭。”",
      "totalCount": 560,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144631&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=42000&rangeEnd=42074",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fe532590813ab9effg011133?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=42000&rangeEnd=42074"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144631_4_25078-25132",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "25078-25132",
      "markText": "既然一个人丧命，只有目睹其死亡，才有一定分量，那么，一亿具尸体，排列在历史的长河中，凭想象也无非是一缕青烟。",
      "totalCount": 540,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144631&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=25078&rangeEnd=25132",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fe532590813ab9effg011133?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=25078&rangeEnd=25132"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144631_4_30233-30321",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "30233-30321",
      "markText": "在一座连普通公务员都有可称道的癖好的城市，鼠疫会真的蔓延开来。准确来说，他还想象不出在鼠疫猖獗的地方，这些癖好能占据什么位置，因此他判断，鼠疫在我们的同胞之间，没有流行的前景。",
      "totalCount": 518,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144631&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=30233&rangeEnd=30321",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fe532590813ab9effg011133?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=30233&rangeEnd=30321"
    },
